{
  "texts": [
    "DWT combined with SVM explained better classifier performance since the refined features are adopted, thus obtaining a high testing accuracy of 92.3%.",
    "The proposed integrated pipeline has given evidence of the effectiveness of CNN combined with DWT and SVM to produce effective and interpretable results even on the medium-sized dataset CKHK-22.",
    "Data augmentation, dropout regularization, early stopping, and proper partitioning of the dataset took care of overfitting.",
    "The data augmentations introduced in the study involved random rotations up to 35°, horizontal flipping, and zooming from a scaling factor of 0.8 to 1.2.",
    "These artificially increased the diversity of the training dataset and ensured that all different kinds of transformations had been seen by the model, thus generalizing well on unseen data."
  ]
}